description:
This is a 31 minute workout called 'A Powerful 30 Minute Grounding Energy Guided Meditation' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Dive into this 30-minute grounding energy guided meditation and unlock the transformative power of reconnecting with your roots.  In just half an hour, you'll embark on a journey that not only releases stress and balances your thoughts but also grounds your energy to its core.  This meditation is your passport to anchoring yourself in the present moment, shedding the chaos of daily life, and fostering an unshakable sense of inner peace.  When you ground your energy, you gain the stability to face life's challenges head-on with a calm and centered mind.  Let this meditation be your compass, guiding you to mental clarity, emotional stability, and a deep wellspring of inner strength.  Don't miss this opportunity to tap into the profound grounding energy you possess.  This is an Original guided meditation recorded by us.  

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!
